    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、{user}さん\nお疲れ様です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Ah‚ {user}-san.\nGood work!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "さくら、莉央さん、お疲れ様\nレッスンの休憩中？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura‚ Rio-san‚ good work.\nAre you on a break from practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "ええ、かれこれ三時間ぶっ通しだったからね\n月ストはまだ、トリエルにしごかれてるけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we've been at it for three hours straight.\nMoon Tempest is still being trained by TRINITYAiLE‚ though.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "三人が戻って来てくれて本当に安心しました\n{user}さん、ありがとうございます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm so relieved that the three of them are back.\nThank you‚ manager-san!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "今三人がここにいるのは\n彼女達を温かく迎え入れた、みんなのおかげだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The reason the three of them are here now is\nthanks to all of you who warmly welcomed them.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.8666669528,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "実際のところ、トリエルに月ストのコーチを\n任せてみて、どう？　調子はいいのかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Actually‚ how's it going with TRINITYAiLE coaching Moon Tempest?\nAre they doing well?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ああ……それなんだけど……\n初日から、凄いことになっててな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ yeah… about that…\nIt's been pretty crazy since day one.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.8475059192,
