    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.5141725858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、どうしたの？　ペース落ちてるわ\nまだまだゴールは先よ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong‚ everyone? You're slowing down.\nThe goal is still a long way off.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.1475059192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 52.2808392525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなこと言われても、はぁ、はぁ\nランニング十キロを、毎日なんて……キツいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if you say that‚ huff‚ huff‚\nten kilometers of running every day… is tough～！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.5141725858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.0475059192
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "え？　でもみんな\n普段、七、八キロぐらいは走っているんでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? But everyone\nusually runs about seven or eight kilometers‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.2141725858,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 69.2808392525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……で、ですけど……\nさすがに毎日では……あ、ありませんから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huff‚ huff… Y-yes‚ but…\nnot every day… n-no…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.8475059192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 77.6808392525
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "けど、ここで限界を超えてこそ\n私達はもっと、強くなれる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But‚ by pushing our limits here‚\nwe can become even stronger…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.4475059192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_comical-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 85.1141725858
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 85.1141725858
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "う、うおおおお！\nそういうことでしたら、や、やってやりますわああ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-yes!\nIf that's the case‚ I-I'll do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 87.6808392525,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 93.5141725859
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "あ、待ってすずちゃん！\nいきなりダッシュは怪我の元――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ wait‚ Suzu-chan!\nSuddenly dashing will lead to injury――",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.9475059192,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 96.6333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "――あ、あ、足がつりましたわあああ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Ow‚ ow‚ my legs are cramping!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
